				<h1></h1>
				<h1>Ho ho ho ! Here are our great christmas gift ideas !</h1>

<p>Christmas is coming and this year you want to plan ahead to find on time the right Christmas gift for your loved ones.</p>

<p>Looking for a unique, fun and surprising Christmas gift ? you&#8217;ve come to the right place !</p>

<p>For you all, <strong>wine lovers</strong>, many wine activities and wine trips gift ideas !</p>
<center><dl class='spip_document_704 spip_documents spip_documents_center'>
<dt><img src='IMG/jpg/143-5.jpg' width='600' height='400' alt='JPEG - 29.5&#160;kb' /></dt>
</dl></center>
<p><br></p>
<h2>Gift ideas : Wine Experiences</h2>

<p><br /><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/-Paris-Day-Trips-.html" class='spip_out'>Loire Valley wine day tour</a></b><br>Your guide will accompany you for the day to uncover the natural beauty of the Loire Valley and its winemaking secrets. You will meet local winemakers and learn more about the wine you will taste. Your guide will describe the history of the vineyards, the methods of the wine making process whilst you discover the vineyard landscapes of the region.</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b>Wine and Chocolate</b> : A wine and chocolate tasting workshop.<br>Perfect for beginners or for experienced chocolate tasters ! <br>You will visit a winery and learn how to expertly pair wine and chocolate, creating new and unexpected tastes that delight the senses.<br>From 40€ per person.</p>
<center><span class='spip_document_703 spip_documents spip_documents_center'>
<img src='IMG/jpg/paques3.jpg' width="400" height="194" alt="" /></span></center>
<p><br></p>
<h2>Gift ideas: Wine trips</h2>
<p><br>Offer one of our wine tasting breaks with an open departure date, see for example the following wine breaks:</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/wine-city-break-saumur.html" class='spip_out'><b>Loire Valley from vines to wines</b></a><br>Let yourself be seduced by the quaint town of Saumur, its famous vineyards and the Royal river. You will enjoy the authentic and wild landscapes while discovering the secrets of the Loire Valley wine.<br>From 190 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Cave-dwelling-and-wines.html" class='spip_out'>Cave Dwelling and wine experience</a></b><br>Discover the wonderful underground world of the Loire Valley by staying in a unique hotel carved into the limestone. You will also get the chance to taste some great wine from the Loire Valley and learn more about the region. A lovely stay all about good food, wine and wild landscapes.<br>From 140 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Burgundy-for-foodies.html" class='spip_out'>Burgundy for foodies</a></b><br>Burgundy : bull’s-eye for foodies and wine enthusiasts !<br class='autobr' />
If you crave life’s full pleasures - the best of the best wines, the most luscious breads to accompany a wealth of assorted gourmet delights - head to Burgundy !<br class='autobr' />
From 585 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Bordeaux-Saint-Emilion-Grands-Crus-156.html" class='spip_out'>Bordeaux and St Emilion Grand Crus</a></b><br class='autobr' />
Renowned for its vineyards, wine certainly runs through the veins of the city and can be experienced in many ways, experience this Wine tasting break with Bleu Vins and uncover the secrets of Bordeaux wines !<br>From 240 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Loire-Valley-for-Foodies.html" class='spip_out'>Loire Valley for foodies</a></b><br>A stay in a unique quaint Wine Estate of the Loire Valley for any food and wine lovers alikes !<br class='autobr' />
From 195 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Languedoc-Roussillon-wine-experience.html" class='spip_out'>Languedoc Roussillon wine experience</a></b><br>Take a trip to Carcassonne to awaken those childhood Disney-style castle fantasies, while experiencing the culinary prowess of France, the great wines and keeping in close quarters to the beaches of the Languedoc Roussillon region.<br>From 380 €</p>

<p><img src="squelettes-dist/puce.gif" width="8" height="11" class="puce" alt="-" />&nbsp;<b><a href="http://www.bleuvins.com/Spa-weekend-and-wine-experience-in-Loire-Valley.html" class='spip_out'>Spa weekend and wine experience in Loire Valley</a></b><br>A wine trip in Loire Valley to unwind, indulge and discover. Relax in the comfort of your stylish 4* Spa Hotel and uncover the secret of <strong>Vouvray wines</strong>.<br>From 245 €</p>
<h2>Gift ideas: Tailor made</h2>

<p><br>Want to give them the choice? We will offer you a christmas gift voucher from the value of your choice. The recipient of the gift will then choose one of our wine tasting breaks or a tailor made experience.</p>
